name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 21, in Xiangtan, Hunan, a girl posted a video saying that she and her father were sexually harassed by a man from a tobacco shop next door while eating barbecue outside. Her father was beaten by several people while defending himself, but he did not fight back because he was worried that fighting back would be considered mutual fighting. After calling the police, the two main people hurriedly left the scene and did not show up again until a few hours later.

content:
"Statistics"
On May 21, the "Sichuan Daily" published an article stating that as of 6 p.m. on May 20, a total of 14,771 couples had registered for marriage in the province, an increase of 13.4% over the number of marriage registrations throughout the day last year, and more than 7 times the average number of marriage registrations per day last year.
However, on May 22 last year, the Sichuan Daily published an article stating that the number of couples who registered for marriage on that day last year was more than 16,000.
